    "body": "This appears to be a problem that occurs at merge transition that prevents remote transactions from getting added to besu's transaction pool.  Short term, this has a very simple mitigation: just restart besu after the merge and remote transactions make it into the txpool just fine.\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n",
