    "body": "We know why Besu has been proposing empty blocks after hitting TTD. It turns out, that incoming transactions cannot be added to the transaction pool unless besu is synced within 100 blocks of its best peer. When one of those peers is a vanilla mainnet peer, and besu is on a shadowfork, that can be a problem.",
